This directory contains the following contributions by Andrei Postnikov

-- Sies2xsf: a collection of Fortran90 tools for converting SIESTA
   results (structure, charge densities, molecular dynamics, phonons,
   Fermi surfaces) for vizualization with XCrySDen.
   (See the README file for details)

-- fmpdos.f: a script to extract individual partial DOS from the
   SIESTA PDOS file

Other useful utilities can be found in Andrei Postnikov's website at
http://www.home.uni-osnabrueck.de/apostnik/download.html


